libqoriq-rcw (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New public API: rcw_preprocess_file(). Runs the embedded mcpp
    preprocessor on a path and returns the expanded text, ready for
    rcw_compile_buffer() / rcw_decompile_buffer(). Lets in-memory
    pipelines avoid the tempfile dance previously needed by callers
    that already had the binary in RAM (e.g. qoriq-rcw --dump).

 -- Vincent Jardin <vjardin@free.fr>  Mon, 13 Apr 2026 14:30:00 +0000

